{"tid":2261594,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[愛情路上，黃藍兩難存]致10/10/2020 叱咤903公子會Phone in聽眾 Isabelle","createTime":"2020-10-28T12:24:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T13:58:06.000Z","uid":76978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6010f407f75eddf484f2433fa1a75b45e6eb425c","tid":2261594,"uid":76978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:24:44.000Z","msg":"有女仔Isabelle Phone in 公子會，討論關於佢男朋友考督察既問題，以下Youtube回應咗95%<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xYBauOxd-eQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxYBauOxd-eQ&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7JNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=ff8eea17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xYBauOxd-eQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但仲有5%漏咗，所以法官大人有野想補充￼<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">當公子會主持問Isabelle 如果要受洗先可以同男朋友（假設系基督教徒）結婚，會點樣選擇？</span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n可能公子會主持太離地，唔明白系中國境內，宗教自由是並<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"violet\">不存在</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"green\">唔好講咩香港同中國有分別<br />\n親中同非親中教會系香港都差別地位啦<br />\n你睇下管浩鳴條契弟</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n陳日君早前自費前往梵蒂岡見教宗，希望教宗停止再次簽署中梵協議<br />\n結果，直到陳樞機上機嗰一刻，教宗仍拒之門外，沒有進行任何形式會面<br />\n<br />\n簽定中梵協議，即系梵蒂岡認可中共所選既中國區天主教教宗，出賣一眾教徒牧師<br />\n當日佢地被逼轉移至地下教會，教宗漠視佢地生命危險與中共建交，是為與虎謀皮<br />\n多年來系中國日復日拆十字架，火燒教會，未來基於中梵協議延長兩年，被出賣的教徒仍要繼續受苦<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"violet\">愛系唔可以戰勝一切，包括宗教/政見</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">因為愛是習近平萬歲</span></strong></span>￼"},{"pid":"ae346dc82be8211a8e676131e96b2c6bb21ef45c","tid":2261594,"uid":76978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}